{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_07_01",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "私をヒロインにした恋愛ゲーム……ですか？",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだ。ゲーム会社の持ち込み企画で、星見プロの\nアイドルを使ったゲームを作ることになったんだよ",
      "startTime": 10.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私がヒロインだなんていいんでしょうか？",
      "startTime": 14.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ヒロインはあくまで『一ノ瀬怜』という\nキャラクターだから、そんなに気負わなくて大丈夫だ",
      "startTime": 21.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "そうかもしれませんが、自分がゲームに出ると思うと\nやっぱり恥ずかしいし、緊張します……",
      "startTime": 29.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "私と疑似恋愛するゲームなんて\n楽しんでもらえるんでしょうか？",
      "startTime": 36.7666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ゲーム会社の人達は「ぜひ怜で」と言っているし\nファンも怜の新しい一面を見られて嬉しいと思うぞ",
      "startTime": 42.7333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですね。分かりました\nそれで私は具体的に何をすればいいんですか？",
      "startTime": 51.7000022888,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8305.714241700003,
          "startTime": 60.0057165305
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ゲームのスタッフから預かったんだが\nこの書類を見てくれないか？",
      "startTime": 58.2267442345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "これは……アンケート、ですか？",
      "startTime": 60.5000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛に関するアンケートだよ。ゲームのシナリオを\n作るに当たって、怜の恋愛観を参考にしたいそうだ",
      "startTime": 69.0613514423,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "私の恋愛観がシナリオに反映されるんですか？\n分かりました、やってみます……",
      "startTime": 78.4333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 82.8000022888,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1133.3343505999949,
          "startTime": 83.9333366394
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-02-000-noon",
      "startTime": 83.8000022888
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "怜、アンケートは書き終わったか？",
      "startTime": 85.16667099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "週末にゲームスタッフと打ち合わせがあるから\nそれまでに提出してほしいんだが……",
      "startTime": 90.6000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、まだ全然埋まってなくて\n書こうとはしてるんですけど……",
      "startTime": 98.3333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "理想のデートとか、恋人と何をしたいかとか\nあまり人に話したことがないので……",
      "startTime": 106.0666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "改まって答えるのが恥ずかしいのか？",
      "startTime": 109.1333376567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……そうです！　恥ずかしいんです！\n私が恥ずかしがったらいけませんか！？",
      "startTime": 117.2666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "だって、私の考える理想の恋愛が\nゲームのシナリオに反映されるんですよ？",
      "startTime": 124.5333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "私の妄想が世間に公表されるみたいで……\nこんなの恥ずかしいに決まってるじゃないですか！",
      "startTime": 132.7000058492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも私は、ずっとダンス漬けの毎日で\n恋愛する暇なんてなかったんです",
      "startTime": 139.8666725159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "だから、好きな人が出来たら何をしたいとか\nあまり考えたことがなくて……",
      "startTime": 147.3168144059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか……\nちなみに、アンケートのどの質問で悩んでいるんだ？",
      "startTime": 151.9333340963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "沢山ありますけど……例えば\n「理想のデートで行きたい場所は？」という質問です",
      "startTime": 160.2666674297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "デートなんてしたことがないので\nどう答えたらいいか分からなくて",
      "startTime": 167.200000763,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "普通はショッピングや映画館って答えるんでしょうけど\nそれが私の理想のデートかと言われると……",
      "startTime": 174.8333340963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "『普通』に囚われなくていいんじゃないか？\nもっと素直に、怜が行きたい場所を書けばいいんだ",
      "startTime": 181.7623840646,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei018.m4a",
      "text": "私が行きたい場所……テーマパーク、とか？",
      "startTime": 185.4333361309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "テーマパークでデートか\n可愛らしくていいじゃないか",
      "startTime": 194.700000763,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei019.m4a",
      "text": "か、可愛いって言わないで下さい！\n余計に恥ずかしくなります！",
      "startTime": 200.2726528608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei020.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも、そうですね……じゃあ、理想のデートは\nテーマパークで……うぅ……",
      "startTime": 209.1333312988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに照れなくてもいいと思うが……\n他にどんな質問で悩んでいるんだ？",
      "startTime": 217.0333340963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei021.m4a",
      "text": "他ですか？　ええと……「恋人に何をしてあげたいか」\nという質問があるんですけど",
      "startTime": 227.000000763,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei022.m4a",
      "text": "私は、好きな人にお弁当を作ってあげて\n一緒に食べたい、って思ったんですが……",
      "startTime": 234.0666674297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei023.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ、やっぱり恥ずかしいです！\nこんな恥ずかしいこと書けません！",
      "startTime": 241.4728997686,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "いいじゃないか。好きな人のためにお弁当を作るなんて\n家庭的で素敵だってみんなに言われると思うぞ",
      "startTime": 248.2333340963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei024.m4a",
      "text": "それが恥ずかしいって言ってるんです！\nもしかして私のことをからかってるんですか！？",
      "startTime": 254.9333340963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "そんな訳ないだろ。しかし、手作り弁当だなんて\n怜は料理得意だったか……？",
      "startTime": 263.4333340963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei025.m4a",
      "text": "自信がある訳じゃないですけど……理想の話ですから\n現実の私とちょっとぐらい違ってもいいじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 271.5666674297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei026.m4a",
      "text": "あくまでこれは私の理想です！\n何か文句ありますか！？",
      "startTime": 278.800000763,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "も、文句だなんてとんでもない！　好きな人のために\n頑張って料理に挑戦する怜は健気で可愛いと思うぞ！",
      "startTime": 284.200000763,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei027.m4a",
      "text": "フォローされればされるほど\n恥ずかしさが増していくんですけど……",
      "startTime": 290.5999905904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei028.m4a",
      "text": "それに、書けない理由は羞恥心だけじゃありません\n「理想の告白のされ方」という質問があるんですが……",
      "startTime": 299.0666572571,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei029.m4a",
      "text": "私は「好きです」と言われるだけで十分なんですけど\nそれだと物足りないし面白みもないですよね？",
      "startTime": 309.8999905904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことはない。とりあえず怜が思うように\n書いてみればいいんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 317.7963486687,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei030.m4a",
      "text": "でも、ゲームになることを考えたら、いっそ私から\n告白された方がファンも嬉しいのではないでしょうか？",
      "startTime": 324.4999783834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei031.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだ。私がどうしたいかより、どうすれば\nファンが喜んでくれるかを考えた方がいいのかも",
      "startTime": 333.9333117168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei032.m4a",
      "text": "その方がゲームも盛り上がるし\n私も恥ずかしがらず客観的に書ける……！",
      "startTime": 340.5666450501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "怜？　どうかしたのか？",
      "startTime": 344.3333106995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
